{"tid":800726,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Telegram更新隱私政策，必要時將交出用戶資料給政府","createTime":"2018-08-31T06:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T07:04:58.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f126795a87eaba7a0b86d5702a1551e435787e06","tid":800726,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:07:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/125600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com.tw%2Fnews%2F125600&d=8o3N58cKbXvOpePAnLU64ZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=5b83c165\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/125600</a><br />\n<br />\nTelegram修改隱私政策，如果執法調查單位能夠證明特定用戶的身份為恐怖分子，就會配合法院要求提供該用戶的IP、電話號碼等資料。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s4.itho.me/sites/default/files/styles/picture_size_large/public/field/image/telegram_0_1.jpg?itok=4RJ_1mRg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs4.itho.me%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fpicture_size_large%2Fpublic%2Ffield%2Fimage%2Ftelegram_0_1.jpg%3Fitok%3D4RJ_1mRg&h=3556bee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6009ba008d1dd3c973d541bfd206ddb0367f1257","tid":800726,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:08:36.000Z","msg":"加密通訊軟體Telegram周四更新隱私政策，未來如果當局能證明是恐怖分子，就會提供用戶IP及電話號碼給當局。<br />\n<br />\n主打用戶隱私安全的Telegram不以用戶資料展示廣告，用戶資料僅用於支援通訊服務所需。他不蒐集用戶真實姓名、性別、年齡或喜好，僅要求用戶提供帳號名稱、代表性相片、基本資訊及電郵信箱，並且還支援二步驟驗證。但是在更新的政策中，Telegram指出，如果接到能證明用戶是恐佈份子嫌犯的法庭文件，就會向相關主管機關揭露用戶IP位址及電話號碼。"},{"pid":"fc28a96e77e46d34f6bcecd16cf3b25a7f05106f","tid":800726,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:09:09.000Z","msg":"不過目前這件事還沒發生過。一如臉書、微軟、Google或其他網路服務業者，如果Telegram被要求交出資料，也會在半年一次的透明度報告揭露。"},{"pid":"4899f8c8b621731d5bb83c9b9f980e33bb605586","tid":800726,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:09:19.000Z","msg":"回教徒又害人"},{"pid":"8b0bf8e5d0905b